OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a rather cloudy day
OL,6,Fwith some patchy light rain. Some
OL,7,Fbright spells will develop in the
OL,8,Fafternoon, especially across Skye and
OL,9,Fthe Western Isles. Feeling rather cool.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA mostly dry evening with
OL,12,Fsome late brightness. Clear spells
OL,13,Fwill develop overnight but becoming
OL,14,Fcloudier with some showers across the
OL,15,Ffar north later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
