OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA mostly dry morning with
OL,6,Fsunny spells but some showers in the
OL,7,Ffar north. Turning cloudy in the
OL,8,Fafternoon with showers becoming
OL,9,Fwidespread. Feeling cool with fresh
OL,10,Fwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,13,Fmixture of sunshine and blustery
OL,14,Fshowers on Tuesday and Wednesday, the
OL,15,Fshowers wintry on the hills. Some rain
OL,16,Fpossible on Thursday. Feeling cold for
OL,17,Fthe time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
